		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>19 W. Baltimore Str.</placeName></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Balto.</placeName> <date>March 20. 1866</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Revd Mr. I. Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Esteemed Sir&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">I deem it my duty<lb/> to inform you&#44; that my ap&#45;<lb/> plication as teacher for the <placeName>Nor&#45;<lb/> folk</placeName> school has so far met<lb/> with success&#44; but to secure same&#44;<lb/> I have been requested to forward<lb/> testimonials of the Gentm.&#44; to whom<lb/> I referred as regards to my ability<lb/> and moral and religious habits.<lb/> Knowing your willingness in<lb/> assisting me to procure said position&#44;<lb/> I therefore most respectfully<lb/> request the favor&#44; anticipating<lb/> immediate attention&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I am with great esteem</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Fraternally Yours</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><persName role="author">E. L. Hess</persName></p>
		</body>
